  "content": "<p data-pid=\"gO1Xl4yX\">【学习】【复习】【笔记】</p><p data-pid=\"udym_OVk\">看到上面这三个【标签】，是不是觉得这是个烂大街的 App 呢？</p><p data-pid=\"fO6bl0Bm\">不急，我再贴上几个标签：</p><p data-pid=\"cYkWbpeq\">【开源】【算法】【卡片】</p><p data-pid=\"u3E7ywEq\">？？？画风突变 ？？？</p><p data-pid=\"nEl5tyYv\">大侠别急！</p><p data-pid=\"k5PeFU5W\">我要介绍的是 Anki —— 一款基于<b>间隔重复</b>算法的<b>开源</b>免费的<b>复习</b> App</p><h2>多图预警</h2><p data-pid=\"Vb8sBmrL\">下图是 Anki 的首页，一列下来全是可以收集【卡片】的【牌组】：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b930229d970836eaeef3c30b4a9a0749_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-original-token=\"v2-2e91265071b7cb42de73d43dcf528b35\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-92d4ba2db640a07cdf7a3ac70f37d32d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b930229d970836eaeef3c30b4a9a0749_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;2280&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-original-token=\"v2-2e91265071b7cb42de73d43dcf528b35\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-92d4ba2db640a07cdf7a3ac70f37d32d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b930229d970836eaeef3c30b4a9a0749_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b930229d970836eaeef3c30b4a9a0749_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"jS2MWXGD\">下图是添加【笔记】，【笔记类型】是你想要的卡片【模板】，Anki 会按照模板帮你把笔记变成【卡片】</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-46b263141ec2c685a3632578b753f60d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-original-token=\"v2-66321f6344cfb1c498ada8884288ff2f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-57edb25dec9851eee1baaf188e541bed_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-46b263141ec2c685a3632578b753f60d_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;2280&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-original-token=\"v2-66321f6344cfb1c498ada8884288ff2f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-57edb25dec9851eee1baaf188e541bed_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-46b263141ec2c685a3632578b753f60d_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-46b263141ec2c685a3632578b753f60d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"1aL-unIE\">划出侧边栏，点开卡片浏览器，可以看到所有的笔记，还可以预览笔记变成卡片后的效果：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-18e52afca502f649b9b8020ae06417e5_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-original-token=\"v2-14726a7934e34ca7a93ed46b4651f374\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-af372b8a19105a2f12037ec8044e1e55_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-18e52afca502f649b9b8020ae06417e5_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;2280&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-original-token=\"v2-14726a7934e34ca7a93ed46b4651f374\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-af372b8a19105a2f12037ec8044e1e55_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-18e52afca502f649b9b8020ae06417e5_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-18e52afca502f649b9b8020ae06417e5_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"8xQYGu-j\">在首页点击牌组开始学习，Anki 就会把一张一张卡片糊到你脸上，让你赶紧回忆答案：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-18cc86a9b4c0fd3de4219c7947c6f051_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-original-token=\"v2-04b58da63f9f10fa53a47b62141dd5b3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4c0cd5ffcd25c0c1112123bd9ed76d0e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-18cc86a9b4c0fd3de4219c7947c6f051_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;2280&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-original-token=\"v2-04b58da63f9f10fa53a47b62141dd5b3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4c0cd5ffcd25c0c1112123bd9ed76d0e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-18cc86a9b4c0fd3de4219c7947c6f051_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-18cc86a9b4c0fd3de4219c7947c6f051_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"QgPyEffb\">在心中准备好答案后可以点显示答案，然后对比检验自己的记忆情况，然后选择这张卡片下一次自测的时间：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b9f9cc7030303888eacc78a14b48de94_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-original-token=\"v2-f9531906709fe82b41e230f5e44a96ad\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6f70850a49bb7ff5785937bdeb7d0dda_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b9f9cc7030303888eacc78a14b48de94_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;2280&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-original-token=\"v2-f9531906709fe82b41e230f5e44a96ad\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6f70850a49bb7ff5785937bdeb7d0dda_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b9f9cc7030303888eacc78a14b48de94_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b9f9cc7030303888eacc78a14b48de94_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"vwzO3H0z\">并且 Anki 有安卓端、mac 端、iOS 端，我主要使用安卓手机，下面是一些截图：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-929f2ce3eeccb14f1e14734e06ddc720_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2200\" data-original-token=\"v2-929f2ce3eeccb14f1e14734e06ddc720\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-929f2ce3eeccb14f1e14734e06ddc720_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;2200&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2200\" data-original-token=\"v2-929f2ce3eeccb14f1e14734e06ddc720\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-929f2ce3eeccb14f1e14734e06ddc720_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-929f2ce3eeccb14f1e14734e06ddc720_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5861650e61872d328650abce4ec2b1c3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2200\" data-original-token=\"v2-5861650e61872d328650abce4ec2b1c3\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5861650e61872d328650abce4ec2b1c3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;2200&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2200\" data-original-token=\"v2-5861650e61872d328650abce4ec2b1c3\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5861650e61872d328650abce4ec2b1c3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5861650e61872d328650abce4ec2b1c3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5db9c458b71fa10d9b5901eed255cdcb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"387\" data-original-token=\"v2-37d51aab5b0507dd45f9341343b092ce\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-5eb34c72ec3e1917240eff44b1a225ee_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-5db9c458b71fa10d9b5901eed255cdcb_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;387&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"387\" data-original-token=\"v2-37d51aab5b0507dd45f9341343b092ce\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.